<dd>
Name of a user or group role.
</dd>

<dt><code>:privileges</code></dt>
<dd>
An array of column privileges the role should be granted to the column.
</dd>

<dt><code>:description</code></dt>
<dd>
A short description of the test.
</dd>

</dl>

